ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT xev.employee_number ,xev.full_name ,xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_emp_parameter( xev.work_base_code_new ,xev.work_base_code_old ,xev.issue_date ,TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate) ) base_code ,xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_emp_parameter( xev.work_base_name_new ,xev.work_base_name_old ,xev.issue_date ,TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate) ) base_name ,xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate current_date ,NULL attach_file_up ,NULL attach_file_up_excerpt ,(SELECT flvv.lookup_code FROM fnd_lookup_values_vl flvv WHERE flvv.lookup_type = 'XXCSO1_SP_ACTING_PO_BASE_CODE' AND flvv.enabled_flag = 'Y' AND NVL(flvv.start_date_active, TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate)) <= TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate) AND NVL(flvv.end_date_active, TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate)) >= TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate) AND flvv.lookup_code = xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_emp_parameter( xev.work_base_code_new ,xev.work_base_code_old ,xev.issue_date ,TRUNC(xxcso_util_common_pkg.get_online_sysdate) ) ) act_po_base_code FROM xxcso_employees_v2 xev WHERE xev.user_id = fnd_global.user_id
